    <td height="30"> <div align="center"><strong>华东师大二附中“十五”校本培训学分评定细则</strong></div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr> 
    <td><p><a href="detailedrules15.asp#1">一、必修课程</a><br>
        <a href="detailedrules15.asp#2">二、选修课程</a><br>
